name: The Tower of Echoes
description: They were once your foes. Now, they are your reflections. In this infinite climb, you face the darkness you left behind.

monsterSequence.name: Charbeast
monsterSequence.description: A relic of fire given cruel sentience.

equipment.name: Protector Plate
equipment.description: Forged by the ancient Vorloran, this plate embodies strength and resilience in battle.

equipment.name: Alloy Shield
equipment.description: A balanced shield forged with slime-alloy for versatility.

equipment.name: Shroud of Shadows
equipment.description: A dark and flowing cape, perfect for evasion.

item.name: Howlglass
item.description: Rings when dropped. Its scream gets louder the deeper it’s mined.

item.name: Aetherore
item.description: Contains thin streaks of something not quite physical. Floats when polished.

item.name: Mindmirror
item.description: Reflects not your face, but your fears. Used in high clairvoyant arts.

item.name: Voidorchid
item.description: Gathers whispers in its core. Said to contain the silence before thunder.

item.name: Ooze Shards
item.description: Slime-coated fragments glimmering with iridescent hues.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Glooplet
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Drifts mindlessly, compelled to consume memories.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Oozeling Wriggler
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Seeps between stones, hunting with ghostlike intent.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Slorbb
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Trembles unnaturally—joy twisted into hunger.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Miremelt
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Spills venomous ichor that scars the floor.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Squelchoid
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Pulses with a sickly glow beneath a warped skin.

monsterSequence.name: The Shadow Gelatinator
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. A grotesque mockery of its perfected form.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Rosemaw
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Petals bloom with blood where it bites.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Petalguard
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Thorns whisper warnings in long-dead tongues.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Thornkin Bulb
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its barbs fester with spectral poison.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Bloomshroud
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Shrouds itself in cursed blossoms to ensnare souls.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Lilylurker
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its roots reach for warmth it no longer feels.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Verdant Snapper
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Snaps not to feed—but to silence.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Murkmancer
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its croak carries echoes from beyond.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Murkbeast
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Disappears into the mist as if never born.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Murkling
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its slime corrodes spirit and flesh alike.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Sludgething
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Glides across the mire without stirring it.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Swampling
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Lures intruders with mimicry of their own voice.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Murklord
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Fungus thrives where the dead once stood.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Slithling
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Strikes from behind veils of shadow and guilt.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Scalelord
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Hisses scripture older than stone.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Scalething
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its echoes warp the tunnel around you.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Venomthing
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Venom drips with necrotic hate.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Hissthing
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Chanted to by ghostly vipers in reverence.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Hisslord
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its gaze pierces into the heart’s decay.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Oathbreaker Fenlord
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Every scar burns with vengeance.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Gnashfang Duelist
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its roar raises the dead in awe.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Ironhide Outcast
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Each trophy bears a name it whispers.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Gorefang Raider
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Strength is its scripture; mercy is void.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Bloodtrail Marauder
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Its laughter splits minds from within.

monsterSequence.name: Shadow Blighthorn Warchief
monsterSequence.description: The corrupted echo of its former self. Fueled by echoes of ancient warcries.
